content: In the dirty white cave, there was a telephone. And a blue fry, and a picture of the loch ness monster jumping over the guy.
And there were three nerd bees sitting on algaes. And two Annoying beds, and a pair of thoroughbreds.
And a obese toy drain, and a gangsta rain. And a tiger and a bite, and a bowl full of heights.
And a fluffy skinny lady who was whispering 'knight'.
Goodnight cave, goodnight guy. Goodnight loch ness monster jumping over the guy. Goodnight light and the blue fry.
Goodnight bees, goodnight algaes. Goodnight beds, and goodnight thoroughbreds. Goodnight obese drain, and goodnight rain.
Goodnight tiger, and goodnight bite. Goodnight nobody, goodnight heights. And goodnight to the skinny lady whispering 'knight'.
